{"tid":2185392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新宿街頭重現無差別打人、跪地求饒等情景 日本人親身感受港警暴","createTime":"2020-09-02T08:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T12:22:08.000Z","uid":322230,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"773a3631ecb826184b8d03c68795ac052ce97a48","tid":2185392,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:35:35.000Z","msg":"日前是太子站「8.31事件」一年，大批港人拒絕遺忘、在站外獻花悼念堅持尋找真相，遠在日本亦有人聲援港人，有人在東京重演「8.31恐襲」事件，將一年前港鐵車廂內市民的慘叫聲、義務急救員在站外要求救人的哀求聲，換個時空重現新宿街頭，讓日本眾民親身感受香港警暴，吸引不少途人拍照及觀看。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7lBF9IQ3UZU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7lBF9IQ3UZU&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=99a5ee62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7lBF9IQ3UZU</a>"},{"pid":"c2ba8c3289787118927dbe5ab6288c1a536628e8","tid":2185392,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a>"},{"pid":"d5e18eb0a98367c942e1e2dd055c72f00d7030a1","tid":2185392,"uid":9845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"日本手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class